OL,6,FA paedophile who raped a girl at least
OL,7,F21 times from the age of nine remains
OL,8,Fat large after being sentenced to 22
OL,9,Fyears in prison.JBrian Green, 74, was
OL,10,Ffound guilty in his absence of five
OL,11,Fcounts of rape following a trial at
OL,12,FLeeds Crown Court in March this year.
OL,14,FHe then failed to attend his
OL,15,Fsentencing hearing on Wednesday, 1
OL,16,FMay, when the lengthy term was handed
OL,17,Fdown.
