OL,6,FDet Insp Paul Greatorex, of the
OL,7,FKirklees District Safeguarding Unit at
OL,8,FWest Yorkshire Police, said: "Brian
OL,9,FGreen has been sentenced in his
OL,10,Fabsence to a lengthy jail term,
OL,11,Freflecting the very serious non-recent
OL,12,Foffences he committed against a young
OL,13,Fand vulnerable child.J"A warrant is
OL,14,Fout for his arrest for failure to
OL,15,Fattend at court and we would ask
OL,16,Fanyone who has seen him or has
OL,17,Finformation about his whereabouts to
OL,18,Fcontact Kirklees police."
